g.title: j1138273574
g.text: 오케이 나 좀 지루해. 아마 좀 궁금하기도 하고? ^_^

g.title: j3896065742
g.text: 원래 본인이 지루한 사람이 잘 지루해하더라.

g.title: j3141454269
g.text: 우리 모두가 너처럼 재미있는 사람일 수만 있다면 좋을텐데 말이지 :)

g.title: j3880305575
g.text: 어느 쪽도 마셔본 적 없어, 솔직히.

g.title: j2533853849
g.text: 미안. 농담이 영 안 좋았어. 어떻게 하면 그대의 지루함을 해결해드릴 수 있을까요, 아가씨?

g.title: j514874018
g.text: 둘 다 괜찮아! 날에 따라 다르지만.

g.title: j1720611493
g.text: 카페인 음료에 우유 넣을래? 아니면 설탕?

g.title: j489659468
g.text: 나이트웨이브. 우주 라디오 쇼 같은 거야.

g.title: j4136716801
g.text: Just another typical day of inter-dimensional cosmic warfare. Can't complain.

g.title: j764483328
g.text: So far, so good. How's your day going?

g.title: j3633449983
g.text: 오오오 너 이 깍쟁이 같으니. 너 걔들 진짜 좋아해?

g.title: j2026538846
g.text: 혹은 그보단... 자경단의 재판을 곁들인 라디오 방송 같은 거지.

g.title: j4129292753
g.text: 혹은 그보단... 청취자들한테 자질구레한 장신구를 제공하는 라디오 방송 같은 거지. ...그리고 총도.

g.title: j3065528399
g.text: best of both worlds, hmm? I respect that.

g.title: j1151667738
g.text: oo la la. black as ur soul, no? ;)

g.title: j1684510453
g.text: I'm watching Quincy pretend he's not annoyed that he missed the bullseye during target practice

g.title: j1212056163
g.text: well, you'd better get back out there and save the world or whatever

g.title: j4050355864
g.text: ur response has been carefully noted

g.title: j193555673
g.text: How far off the mark was he?

g.title: j3280075297
g.text: I think you mean save the universe.

g.title: j2824271068
g.text: like an inch off the center lol. end of the world, right?

g.title: j1569384474
g.text: the annoyed part or the pretending not to be annoyed part?

g.title: j2955015285
g.text: haha what made you think I was lying?

g.title: j3081572031
g.text: You like their music too, right?

g.title: j2756182097
g.text: oof he's been frowning silently into the void for like 5 mins. I should at least try to cheer him up.

g.title: j2767043483
g.text: wellll I've heard a lot of "pop isn't real music" and "hating things u like makes me unique"

g.title: j2273417251
g.text: but enough about me! what's music like in the future?

g.title: j3889880374
g.text: ur telling me I have TWO roguish perfectionists to worry about now?

g.title: j1590457429
g.text: what a wonderfully mysterious thing to say

g.title: j1932166822
g.text: pretty hard on yourself, are u? that's too bad. u deserve better :)

g.title: j2925906686
g.text: Hey, anyone who says that about things you enjoy totally sucks.

g.title: j2807007803
g.text: You ever heard of a Shawzin?

g.title: j3866991193
g.text: On-lyne makes it look ez, but pop music takes a lot of skill.

g.title: j3544718375
g.text: Yeah, the skill of playing the same four chords... over and over...

g.title: j3410330466
g.text: True. Making it seem effortless is actually part of the challenge.

g.title: j1405722518
g.text: im totally telling Arthur u said that ;)

g.title: j3673953550
g.text: It's a "future" instrument. Sounds like... I actually have no way to describe it. A storybook?

g.title: j560063131
g.text: sounds beautiful ^_^ I'd like to hear it some time

g.title: j1917660979
g.text: let's talk after you've written your hit song, maestro :)

g.title: j379518954
g.text: (unless you dont care bc i will so tell Arthur u said that)

g.title: j3754156620
g.text: I'll just have to bring you to the future with me.

g.title: j3446764812
g.text: I'll just have to bring one to the past with me.

g.title: j2044046851
g.text: hey, you're great at curing boredom :) thx

g.title: j2257710264
g.text: Yikes. I'd better not walk into that. Lol.

g.title: j799517332
g.text: but fr thx for saying that ^_^ and curing my boredom

g.title: j3894506403
g.text: Ah. Well, no. Not like an octopus. More like a guitar.

g.title: j788346283
g.text: No bass like octopus bass, I guess. Lol.

g.title: j1991740821
g.text: aaw I was ready to hear that in the future we learned to commune with the ocean's greatest musicians!

g.title: j406273159
g.text: I suppose that of all sea creatures, the octopus would definitely be the best musician.

g.title: j1242136207
g.text: I wish I could tell you the future was that cool.

g.title: j2948644857
g.text: I think I'll like future music ^_^

g.title: j3963121846
g.text: well ur there, so it's at least kind of cool

g.title: j2048161463
g.text: what about whales? those beautiful voices would make them strong contenders too

g.title: j1240798919
g.text: omg Amir's about to get a new high score in Ollie’s Crash Course! can't miss this.
